% Rust Language Ontology - CNL Format
% Extends oo_ontology.cnl with Rust-specific concepts

% File/Module types
Every rust-compilation-unit is a compilation-unit.
Every rust-module is a module.

% Type definitions
Every rust-struct is a struct.
Every rust-enum is an enum.
Every rust-trait is a trait.
Every rust-union is a union.
Every rust-type-alias is a type-alias.

% Members
Every rust-function is a function.
Every rust-method is a method.
Every rust-field is a field.
Every rust-enum-member is an enum-member.

% Parameters
Every rust-parameter is a parameter.

% Import
Every rust-use is an import.
Every rust-extern-crate is an import.

% Control flow
Every rust-return-statement is a return-statement.

% Other
Every rust-variable is a variable.
Every rust-constant is a field.
Every rust-static is a field.
Every rust-reference is a reference.
Every rust-attribute is an attribute.
Every rust-anonymous-function is an anonymous-function.

% Rust-Specific Concepts
Every impl-block is a class.
Every trait-impl is a class.
Every macro-definition is a function.
Every lifetime-parameter is a parameter.

% Code Smells
Every rust-god-struct is a god-class.
Every rust-long-function is a long-method.
